== ARTICLE XV

=== Finance Committee

(((Finance Committee)))(((Convention, Finance Committee)))Resolved, the General Convention of the IWW shall nominate a standing Finance Committee. The Finance Committee shall be elected by referendum. It shall include:

. Up to five members, who must be IWW members in good standing, elected by the General Convention.
. The GST (ex-officio)
. The GEB chair (ex-officio)

The Finance Committee will:

. Advise the General Executive Board on financial matters
. Assist in preparing an operating budget
. Advise General Headquarters on bookkeeping and accounting procedures
. Make a report to the membership at least once per fiscal year.

